dataIdInfo.idAbs: The dataset represents the Operational Zones Level 2 of Somalia. These are only found in certain urban areas. Operational zones are not official administrative features.

dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found and fixed by ITOS: 1. 10 OPZ2 units in Banadir had Admin2 attribution that conflicted with their spatial location. These errors were corrected in this version 2. Small nesting errors with other layers were fixed
